ion": "It has been said that this is more beneficial for the one who gives bad words if he wants to correct himself then should take a bowl and should write AL-HAMEE-DO on all the inside portions, and should drink water in that bowl, inshallah will be away from that bad habit.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Bayaan kiya gaya hai keh yeh us shakhs ke liye ziyadah munaasib hai keh jo gaaliya’n (bad words) deta ho agar yeh shakhs khud apni islaah chahta ho to kisi bartan mein murabba (pyaale ke chaaro’n taraf) surat mein AL-HAMEE-DO likh kar us mein paani peeye ya jis ki islaah maqsood (maqsad) ho us ko pilaaye to inshallah bohot jald woh us buri aadat se dur ho jaayega.", "UrduDescription": "بیان کیا گیا ہے کہ یہ اس شخص کے لئے زیادہ مناسب ہے کہ جو گالیاں دیتا ہوا اگر یہ شخص خود اپنی اصلاح چاہتا ہو تو کسی برتن میں مربع صورت میں ’’اَلْحَمِیْدُ‘‘  لکھ کر اس میں پانی پیئے یا جس کی اصلاح مقصود ہو اس کو پلائے تو انشاء اللہ بہت جلد وہ اس بری عادات سے دور ہوجائے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": 